<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Two-Factor Authentication Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .email-body h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin: 15px 0;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .code-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #0066cc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            color: #0066cc;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .code-validity {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .warning-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .email-footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="{$logo_path}logo_head.png" alt="{$shop_name} Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>🔒 Two-Factor Authentication</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h2>{if $customer_gender == 'f'}Dear Ms.{elseif $customer_gender == 'm'}Dear Mr.{else}Dear{/if} {$customer_name},</h2>
            
            <p>You have requested a security code for two-factor authentication at <strong>{$shop_name}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="code-box">
                <div class="code">{$code}</div>
                <div class="code-validity">
                    <strong>Valid for {$validity_minutes} minutes</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Enter this code on the login page to complete the login process.</p>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><strong>⚠ Security Notice:</strong> If you did not request this code, please ignore this email and change your password for security reasons.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Your {$shop_name} Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>This email was generated automatically. Please do not reply directly to this message.</p>
            <p>&copy; {$smarty.now|date_format:"%Y"} {$shop_name}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
